<p>Trivia:
I have <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erdos_number">Erdös</a> number 4: Me –&gt; Volker Betz –&gt; Peter Mörters –&gt; David Preiss –&gt; Paul Erdös, and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bacon_number">Bacon number</a> 3: Me –(G103)–&gt; Patrick Niknejad –(Harry Potter)–&gt; Gary Oldman –(Criminal Law)–&gt; Kevin Bacon.</p>

<p>This gives me an <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erd%C5%91s%E2%80%93Bacon_number">Erdös-Bacon</a> number of 7.</p>

